levels.name: Erosion-Resistant Coating Application Device
levels.description: Grants immunity to 'Erosion' to the allied unit in the tile ahead ('Erosion': Reduced ASPD, receives a certain amount of <$ba.dt.erosion>Corrosion Damage</> every second and receives additional <$ba.dt.erosion>Corrosion Damage</> proportional to the enemy's ATK when attacked)
